object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT distinct
acx_coverage_item_row_id, 
acx_coverage_item_batch_id, 
acx_coverage_item_row_md5checksum, 
acx_coverage_item_row_effective_start_datetime,

CROSS JOIN current_batch cb;

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

object.customQuery:
select
	source_system_row_id,
	coverage_item_id,
	coverage_item_row_md5checksum,
	coverage_item_row_effective_end_datetime 
from
	$$refined_schema.coverage_items
where
	coverage_item_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
order by source_system_row_id, coverage_item_id ;

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: o_update_flag
fields.expression:
IIF(NOT ISNULL(tgt_source_system_row_id) AND
NOT ISNULL(row_id) AND
tgt_coverage_item_row_md5checksum <> src_md5_hash_value
, 'U','X')
